{"tid":2510643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國電視驚曝可掃描所有網絡設備並自動回傳數據","createTime":"2021-04-30T09:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T13:31:26.000Z","uid":112748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1c8c07f85073489dbf184aaee31ea4c3f77411","tid":2510643,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"（本台記者韓梅綜合報導）一中國網友最近在技術性社交媒體&ldquo;V2EX&rdquo;上曝光自己發現家中電視可以自動掃描所有網絡設備，並自動回傳數據的過程。<br />\n<br />\n這位網友表示，因爲覺得電視速度很慢，就打開系統看開了哪些功能，發現有項功能&ldquo;勾正數據服務&rdquo;，&ldquo;完全不知道是乾什麼的&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n於是這位網友就研究了一下，赫然發現這東西每隔10分鐘就會掃描一遍他家所有連接網絡的設備，並自動將數據傳到指定網站，&ldquo;把 hostname 、mac 、ip 甚至網絡延遲時間全傳回去了，還探測周圍的wifi SSID 名稱、mac 地址也打包傳到這個gz-data .com 的域名&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n網友驚問：&ldquo;也就是說，家裏有什麼智能設備、手機在不在家、誰來家裏連網了、周圍鄰居wifi 叫什麼名，隨時採集上傳，確定這不是間諜服務？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n網友還透露，他家電視是創維，使用安卓系統。<br />\n<br />\n文章底下網友紛紛留言表示關注。有說自己也受到驚嚇的，也有請教技術細節的：<br />\n<br />\n這種電視我家都是不敢連網的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;能卸載（解除安裝）嗎？我家也是這種系統&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我家小米路由器，<a href=\"http://一直請求API.miwifi.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E8%AB%8B%E6%B1%82API.miwifi.com&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=e500a02b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">一直請求API.miwifi.com</a>域名，3秒請求一次不知道乾什麼，害怕.jpg&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;所以我一直很反感智能家居（家庭自動化）&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;所以隱私就是這麼被竊取的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n另外還有行家提供解決方案：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;所以我是用主路由禁止小米路由器聯網。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;所有設備全部使用隨機化 mac 地址，對國產設備單獨 vlan 隔離，無需訪問互聯網的一律禁止互聯網連接，無需訪問局域網的只給一個點對點連接。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;要對付這個很簡單嘛，VLAN 隔離一下，然後在隔離 VLAN 裏麵造兩千個隨機 MAC 地址的設備，每天換一波；電視如果有 WiFi 的話，要麼直接把天線拔了，要麼弄個屏蔽罩罩起來，裏麵塞個 ESP8266 之類的東西隨機發幾百個 SSID 每天換一波。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n更多留言則對國產電子設備表示不信任，甚至厭惡：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;所以別買國產互聯網電視（網絡電視），買了也別連網&rdquo;、&ldquo;常規用戶追蹤手段&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;垃圾國產，就這一羣人還整天吹支持國產，恨不得內褲給你扒了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;萬物互聯&times;，萬物監控?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;不稀奇...在理解範圍內...中國特色&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：元明清"},{"pid":"edbf0888ebce87e0c647181811d336fc7639a727","tid":2510643,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:52:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/498914?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F498914%3Flang%3Db5&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=b99f6cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/498914?lang=b5</a>"},{"pid":"a5b71bd468471344906ee5b8fbe5f38f085ce98f","tid":2510643,"uid":262557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"Big brother"},{"pid":"b6afba3d3be1e50c6b4da1d13d6822aba64c6b0c","tid":2510643,"uid":59511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"用小米路由器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都俾人二穴中出咗啦，唔爭在口爆埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87973129ac4f674c90f78c275342d64b9e374067","tid":2510643,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:08:34.000Z","msg":"算係新聞？"},{"pid":"43dd3a3f3eb2834fc898c5b536fa3ddc5e486e9e","tid":2510643,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87973129ac4f674c90f78c275342d64b9e374067","tid":2510643,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:08:34.000Z","msg":"算係新聞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:09:14.000Z","msg":"old news so 唔識串"},{"pid":"665cc8339fa118ea17468af9a3b9b55fc63d7e73","tid":2510643,"uid":360907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:11:03.000Z","msg":"人黎 同我捉曬呢班友去抄家<br />\n又抹黑中國、勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd305fbbadcbe14605215e613fcebe651e2c89e7","tid":2510643,"uid":79869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"Old news 好多年前機頂盒時代已經做緊...<br />\n人人都知大陸d機頂盒有後門...構成殭屍網絡<br />\n有需要時會借左你屋企個網絡發動DDoS..."},{"pid":"955fe57e4b40aafa588c6ad045e64a70d94dc492","tid":2510643,"uid":63287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"以前icable 用電視線上網"},{"pid":"b0fde29b50a866544661948325efe45f0b4bca73","tid":2510643,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:20:36.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;要對付這個很簡單嘛，VLAN 隔離一下，然後在隔離 VLAN 裏麵造兩千個隨機 MAC 地址的設備，每天換一波；電視如果有 WiFi 的話，要麼直接把天線拔了，要麼弄個屏蔽罩罩起來，裏麵塞個 ESP8266 之類的東西隨機發幾百個 SSID 每天換一波。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n雖然看不懂 但好像很厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416cc188b09a9e4e16c22cf66b39a5d489d4f3ef","tid":2510643,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"hide ssid 有冇用"},{"pid":"d91548cca7a89afa7ecd92ef1653c2953617db1d","tid":2510643,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6afba3d3be1e50c6b4da1d13d6822aba64c6b0c","tid":2510643,"uid":59511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"用小米路由器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都俾人二穴中出咗啦，唔爭在口爆埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:30:23.000Z","msg":"鄰居有用會唔會中伏"},{"pid":"89f7246e3657688ec1f4fbf27d01ecacd25e1d39","tid":2510643,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:33:20.000Z","msg":"支那製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305f8329935561a674783e5c609b90c39d6223e2","tid":2510643,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91548cca7a89afa7ecd92ef1653c2953617db1d","tid":2510643,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6afba3d3be1e50c6b4da1d13d6822aba64c6b0c","tid":2510643,"uid":59511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"用小米路由器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都俾人二穴中出咗啦，唔爭在口爆埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:30:23.000Z","msg":"鄰居有用會唔會中伏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:28:16.000Z","msg":"唔知，有無IT友補腦？"},{"pid":"a0eda4fee7cb649823308d74856a7537cea9c6dc","tid":2510643,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:29:56.000Z","msg":"呢d新聞同馬英九看錶都冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c981a460ff46157d4eec74e2e4407bac32875c9","tid":2510643,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:31:26.000Z","msg":"依家香港同支那買上網電視已經好危險<br />\n<br />\n買個chromecast仲穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}